title: Homecoming queen fills in as Franklin H.S. placekicker
text:
Homecoming queen fills in as Franklin H.S. placekicker It is a rush when the fans go crazy after you make one, kicker says UPDATED 3:22 PM EDT Oct 17, 2015 A Large Text Photos 
The homecoming queen at Franklin High School suited up Friday night to take the field with the football team. Related Police to students: School threats... 
Jade Paris, who is a senior at Franklin, filled in as the placekicker for the Wildcats. 
"It is like a really good stress reliever, and it is just a rush when the fans go crazy after you make one. There's nothing like it,‚Äù Paris said. 
Paris has converted 9 of her 11 extra points this season.
